Bikeshed time! I feel that the bool adds complexity to the logic. I would rather just use an actual comment to indicate what the condition is for:<p><pre><code>  int padded_size(int size)
  {
    int remainder = size % 2048;

    // do we even need padding?
    if (remainder == 0) {
      return size;
    }
    return size + (2048 - remainder);
  }</code></pre>
